config RADIO_RTC6226
	tristate "Richtek RTC6226 FM radio receiver support"
	depends on I2C && VIDEO_DEV
	help
	  This is a driver for I2C devices with the Richtek RTC6226
	  FM radio receiver chip.

	  Say Y here if you want to connect this type of radio to your
	  system via I2C bus.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here:
	  the module will be called radio-rtc6226-i2c.

